com.firebase.authwrapper.providers.common.properties

Class ProviderProperties

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.firebase.authwrapper.providers.common.properties.ProviderProperties

  • public class ProviderProperties
extends java.lang.Object

    This Properties class hold all the properties needed for initialize and define instances of different Provider

    The properties are needed when creating new providers instance using the factory method createAuthProvider in order to build all different provider, each one with different configuration.
